  "title": "Clinical Associate",
  "description": "<p><strong>Clinical Associate</strong><br /></p><p>You will provide clinical care / procedures to the patients under the supervision of senior doctors. You will be required to perform night duties and work on weekends/public holidays according to department roster. You will work alongside nursing, allied health and pharmacist colleagues in a team-based setting to provide comprehensive and holistic patient care.</p><p>We have vacancies in the following disciplines:</p><p>Medicine</p><p>Anaesthesia</p><p>Radiology</p><p>Otolaryngology (ENT)</p><p>Emergency Medicine</p><p>Surgery</p><p>Orthopaedic Surgery</p><p>Ophthalmology<br /></p><p><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Basic medical qualification with at least 3 years’ post Housemanship working experiences;</li><li>Those with relevant postgraduate qualification will have an advantage;</li><li>Be in active clinical practice in the past 3 years in the relevant discipline;</li><li>Able to work independently in a fast-paced environment with strong adaptability to changes;</li><li>Strong command of spoken and written English;</li><li>Registered (or meet registration criteria) with Singapore Medical Council.</li></ul>",
